    given-names: SaiPranay
license: MIT
repository-code: https://github.com/PranayS676/KVOptBench
abstract: KVOptBench is a cache-aware frontier LLM inference benchmark and strategy optimizer for studying KV cache behavior, prefix caching, prefill/decode bottlenecks, KV quantization, KV offload, speculative decoding, and quality-latency tradeoffs.
keywords:
  - llm-inference
  - kv-cache
  - prefix-caching
  - vllm
  - sglang
  - speculative-decoding
  - benchmark
  - frontier-models
